<title>Defines</title>
<section>
  <title>Files</title>
  <itemizedlist spacing="compact">
    <listitem>
      <simpara>

	<ulink
	url="&topsrc/os/kernel/defines/MLSStatistics.H"><filename>MLSStatistics.H</filename></ulink>:
	enables hardware dependant statistics.

      </simpara>
    </listitem>
    <listitem>
      <simpara>

	<ulink url="&topsrc/os/kernel/defines/inout.H"><filename>inout.H</filename></ulink>:
	defines what input output devices should be used.

      </simpara>
    </listitem>
    <listitem>
      <simpara>

	<ulink
	url="&topsrc/os/kernel/defines/mem_debug.H"><filename>mem_debug.H</filename></ulink>:
	Enables debugging options for memory.

      </simpara>
    </listitem>
    <listitem>
      <simpara>

	<ulink
	url="&topsrc/os/kernel/defines/optimizations.H"><filename>optimizations.H</filename></ulink>:
	defines varios flags which drive optimizations done for
	performance measurements.

      </simpara>
    </listitem>
    <listitem>
      <simpara>

	<ulink
	url="&topsrc/os/kernel/defines/paging.H"><filename>paging.H</filename></ulink>:
	Controls whether paging (pageout/swap) is on and which daemons
	should be run.

      </simpara>
    </listitem>
    <listitem>
      <simpara>

	<ulink
	url="&topsrc/os/kernel/defines/sim_bugs.H"><filename>sim_bugs.H</filename></ulink>:
	defines varios flags which drive workarounds for simulators we
	are currently using.

      </simpara>
    </listitem>
    <listitem>
      <simpara>

	<ulink
	url="&topsrc/os/kernel/defines/template_bugs.H"><filename>template_bugs.H</filename></ulink>:
	defines various flags which drive workarounds for current
	compiler bugs involving templates.

      </simpara>
    </listitem>
    <listitem>
      <simpara>

	<ulink
	url="&topsrc/os/kernel/defines/use_expedient.H"><filename>use_expedient.H</filename></ulink>:
	Controls whether to use expedient or optimized implementations
	of various Dispatcher- and Exception-level paths.

      </simpara>
    </listitem>
    <listitem>
      <simpara>

	<ulink url="&topsrc/os/kernel/defines/linux_support.H"><filename>linux_support.H</filename></ulink>:
	Controls linux support on K42.

      </simpara>
    </listitem>
    <listitem>
      <simpara>

	<ulink url="&topsrc/os/kernel/defines/sched_options.H">
	  <filename>sched_options.H</filename>
	</ulink>
	: Controls scheduling features.

      </simpara>
    </listitem>
    <listitem>
      <simpara>

	<ulink url="&topsrc/os/kernel/defines/experimental.H">
	  <filename>experimental.H</filename>
	</ulink>
	: Controls experimental features.

      </simpara>
    </listitem>
  </itemizedlist>
</section>
<section>
  <title>Overview</title>
  <para>

    Places to put any conditional compilation flags to get dependacies
    on real files rather than makefile options

  </para>
</section>
